The Block Australia - Glasshouse Series 9 Episode 39

Each series on The Block the somewhat cocky new contestants come in thinking they know exactly how it's all going to work.
Michael & Carlene, Gold Coast, QLD
Project Manager/Chippy and Communications Officer, both 31
Jenna & Chris, Sydney, NSW
Video Editor, 26 and Cabinet Maker, 24, both self-employed
Darren & Dee, Melbourne, VIC
Ex-AFL footballer/studying to be a builder, 32 and Mother, 42
Shannon & Simon, TAS, raised Coffs Harbour, NSW
Painter, 35 and Plumber, 28
Karstan & Max, Newcastle, NSW
Miner, 26 and Major Event Planner, 24

The teams have a chance to win some high end furniture for their living and dining rooms with Shelley's Australian Made Challenge. Using Aussie made items they must recreate their living or dining area. This time, Shaynna Blaze is the judge.
